definition: many/much/often/a lot of/numerous/more/in excess/how (to what extent)/multi-/Taiwan pr. [duo2] when it means "how"
value/(to be) worth/to happen to/to be on duty

sentences.english: A multivalued property behaves programmatically as an array of values.
sentences.chinese: 多值屬性在編程上表現爲一組數值。

sentences.english: It had the additional advantage of supporting multivalued fields.
sentences.chinese: 它還有支持多值字段的優勢。

sentences.english: A coincidence theorem on set-valued mapping is directly derived according to the section theorem.
sentences.chinese: 並且用截口定理直接證明了多值映射的一個重合定理。

sentences.english: The use of multi-value context variables is limited to one per staff query element.
sentences.chinese: 多值上下文變量的使用限於每個人員查詢元素一個。

sentences.english: This paper shows that lower semicontinuous accretive and monotone operators T cannot be multivalued.
sentences.chinese: 證明下半連續增生和單調映射不可是多值的。

sentences.english: The conception and theorem of fuzzy embedded multivalued dependency are also introduced.
sentences.chinese: 介紹了模糊嵌入多值依賴的概念及公理系統。

sentences.english: It has been shown that the use of the new circuit can reduce the size of the MVPLA.
sentences.chinese: 這種電路減少了所設計多值可編程邏輯陣列的規模。

sentences.english: It is now possible to model exceptions and multivalued attributes.
sentences.chinese: 現在可以對模型異常和多值屬性進行功能增強了。

sentences.english: The existence of random attractors for multi-value random semiflows was studied.
sentences.chinese: 該文研究多值隨機半流的隨機吸引子的存在性。

sentences.english: In this paper the definition of Riemann integral haus been given by using the limit of many-valued function.
sentences.chinese: 本文試圖用多值函數的極限說明黎曼積分的定義。

sentences.english: You will notice that in this case, the check box specifying multi-valued data is selected.
sentences.chinese: 您會注意到指定多值數據的複選框被選中了。

sentences.english: Be aware that this is the reason for the restricted number of multi-value context variables.
sentences.chinese: 請注意，這就是限制多值上下文變量數量的原因。

sentences.english: It is generally specified in conjunction with the multi-valued check box discussed earlier.
sentences.chinese: 它通常是和早期談論的多值複選框一起指定。

sentences.english: In this paper, a new coincidence theorem for multivalued mappings of upper hemicontinuous is given.
sentences.chinese: 本文對弱上半連續多值映象給出了一個新的疊合定理。

sentences.english: In instrument study field there is little study of multiple-valued instrument.
sentences.chinese: 在儀器研究領域中很少見到有關多值儀器的研究。
